             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am employed by Mr. Killgore, in <placeName id="t17910413-29-crimeloc161">Friday-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17910413-29-crimeloc161" type="placeName" value="Friday-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17910413-29-crimeloc161" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-29-off159 t17910413-29-crimeloc161"></join>; a Scotch warehouse. Between the 2d and 4th of April the warehouse was broke open; we lost four pieces of printed cotton; I saw them laying there on the Saturday night; on the Monday morning I saw the window was broke, and I missed the four pieces; the warehouse is under the dwelling-house; the pane of glass was broke, and the glass laying on the counter, and these two hooks; the window looks into the street.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17910413-29-person352">
                  JOHN
                   TYLER
               <interp inst="t17910413-29-person352" type="surname" value="TYLER"></interp>
