                  </persName>
            , <rs id="t17910413-29-verdict163" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910413-29-verdict163" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17910413-29-punish164" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910413-29-punish164" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-29-defend349 t17910413-29-punish164"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Court to Collier. The Gentlemen of the Jury have done, undoubtedly, perfectly right in acquitting you; though, privately speaking, I very much suspect your guilt: the rules of administering justice have protected you more than your own innocence; take care the future course of your life is conducted better than that which is by-gone, or else you will be very soon cut off; take care, remember and return God thanks for the mercy that is now shewn you.</p>
